messages.messageBody:
**I went to high school with a guy who often came to school dressed as
Wonder
Woman. He also mostly did murals of her in art. I have no idea how he
turned
out.**

Well... in the last year or two I read a newspaper feature about a man
who had been totally obsessed with Wonder Woman in his youth who had
just been appointed editor or chief writer for the new Wonder Woman
comic. So there really is a perfect job out there for everyone!

(You could try googling your friend's name and see if you can find any
evidence of him. A man in a Wonder Woman costume should leave a fiery
trail. <g>)

Betsy
